question_response.DESCR: Goes to toilet, gets on and off, arranges clothes, cleans genital area without help.

question.DESCR: Transferring

question_response.DESCR: Moves in and out of bed or chair unassisted (mechanical transfer aids are acceptable)

question.DESCR: Continence

question_response.DESCR: Exercises complete self-control over urination and defecation.

question.DESCR: Feeding

Needs partial or total help with feeding or requires parenteral feeding.

question.DESCR: Shopping

Needs to be accompanied on any shopping trip

Travels on public transportation when accompanied by another
